        "body": "## Overview\r\nAdds a new Harbor task: `json-field-sorter`.\r\n\r\n## Description\r\nThis task requires agents to read a JSON file containing a list of objects and sort them based on a given numeric field (`score`) in ascending order. \r\nThe input file is located at `/app/input.json` and the output must be written to `/app/output.json`.\r\n\r\n## Changes Made\r\n- Created `task.toml` defining the task metadata and permissions.\r\n- Added [instruction.md](cci:7://file:///Users/shikharsingh/Desktop/Harbor%20assignment/harbor/harbor_tasks/json-field-sorter/instruction.md:0:0-0:0) with the problem statement and example input/output.\r\n- Configured the Dockerfile with base environment settings.\r\n- Provided `input.json` containing test data (objects with `id`, `name`, `score`, and `department`).\r\n- Implemented `solve.sh` reference solution using `jq`.\r\n- Added test scripts (`test.sh` and `test_outputs.py`) for validation.\r\n\r\n## Testing\r\n- Verified `test.sh` passes successfully with the reference solution.\r\n\r\n<!-- devin-review-badge-begin -->\r\n\r\n---\r\n\r\n<a href=\"https://app.devin.ai/review/laude-institute/harbor/pull/912\" target=\"_blank\">\r\n  <picture>\r\n    <source media=\"(prefers-color-scheme: dark)\" srcset=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-dark.svg?v=1\">\r\n    <img src=\"https://static.devin.ai/assets/gh-open-in-devin-review-light.svg?v=1\" alt=\"Open with Devin\">\r\n  </picture>\r\n</a>\r\n<img width=\"849\" height=\"265\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-03-01 at 2 18 20 AM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/15e4b13f-afd4-446b-8c33-1402c4ed8699\" />\r\n<img width=\"854\" height=\"336\" alt=\"Screenshot 2026-03-01 at 2 19 14 AM\" src=\"https://github.com/user-attachments/assets/73146483-1d76-4e60-91c6-60a64e1864f1\" />\r\n\r\n",
